msgid "Terms of use"
msgstr "Telerau Defnyddio"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/actor-terms-of-use.html.twig:16
msgid ""
"The Use a lasting power of attorney (LPA) service lets you create\n"
"                        ‘access codes’ to give to professionals or organisations so "
"they can view an online summary of an <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</"
"abbr>.\n"
"                        For example, financial institutions, medical professionals, "
"and care organisations."
msgstr ""
"Mae’r gwasanaeth Defnyddio atwrneiaeth arhosol (LPA) yn eich galluogi i greu\n"
"                        ‘codau mynediad’ i’w rhoi i bobl broffesiynol neu "
"sefydliadau fel y gallant weld crynodeb ar-lein o <abbr title=\"atwrneiaeth "
"arhosol\">LPA</abbr>. \n"
"                        Er enghraifft, sefydliadau ariannol, gweithwyr proffesiynol "
"meddygol a sefydliadau gofal."

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/actor-terms-of-use.html.twig:22
msgid ""
"The service is for donors and attorneys on an <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney"
"\">LPA</abbr>."
msgstr ""
"Mae’r gwasanaeth ar gyfer rhoddwyr ac atwrneiod ar <abbr title=\"atwrneiaeth "
"arhosol\">LPA</abbr>."

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/actor-terms-of-use.html.twig:25
msgid ""
"You should be able to use this service instead of showing someone the original paper "
"<abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr>."
msgstr ""
"Dylech allu defnyddio’r gwasanaeth hwn yn lle gorfod dangos fersiwn papur y <abbr "
"title=\"atwrneiaeth arhosol\">LPA</abbr> i rywun."

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/actor-terms-of-use.html.twig:33
msgid ""
"You cannot use a download or print out of the\n"
"                        <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr> summary "
"in place of the original paper\n"
"                        <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr> or "
"instead of giving someone an access code"
msgstr ""
"Ni allwch ddefnyddio copi wedi’i lawrlwytho neu gopi wedi’i argraffu o’r \n"
"                        crynodeb <abbr title=\"atwrneiaeth arhosol\">LPA</abbr> ar-"
"lein yn lle fersiwn papur y \n"
"                        <abbr title=\"latwrneiaeth arhosol\">LPA</abbr> neu yn lle "
"rhoi cod mynediad i rywun"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/actor-terms-of-use.html.twig:41
msgid ""
"By using this service you agree to these terms of use and the\n"
"                        <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://www.gov.uk/help/terms-"
"conditions\">GOV.UK terms and conditions</a>."
msgstr ""
"Trwy ddefnyddio’r gwasanaeth hwn rydych yn cytuno i’r telerau defnyddio hyn a \n"
"                        <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://www.gov.uk/help/terms-"
"conditions\">thelerau ac amodau GOV.UK</a>."

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/actor-terms-of-use.html.twig:45
msgid "Your responsibilities as an attorney"
msgstr "Eich cyfrifoldebau fel atwrnai"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/actor-terms-of-use.html.twig:47
msgid ""
"If you’re an attorney, remember that using this service to give someone access to a "
"summary of the\n"
"                        <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr>, is the "
"same as using the original paper <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</"
"abbr>."
msgstr ""
"Os ydych yn atwrnai, cofiwch bod defnyddio’r gwasanaeth hwn i roi mynediad i rywun i "
"grynodeb o’r \n"
"                        <abbr title=\"atwrneiaeth arhosol\">LPA</abbr>, yr un fath â "
"defnyddio fersiwn papur y <abbr title=\"atwrneiaeth arhosol\">LPA</abbr>."

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/actor-terms-of-use.html.twig:52
msgid ""
"When using an <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr> you must always "
"follow the legal responsibilities you\n"
"                        agreed to when you signed the <abbr title=\"lasting power of "
"attorney\">LPA</abbr>. For example, you must always:"
msgstr ""
"Pan fyddwch yn defnyddio <abbr title=\"atwrneiaeth arhosol\">LPA</abbr> mae’n rhaid "
"i chi wastad ddilyn y cyfrifoldebau cyfreithiol y bu i chi\n"
"                        gytuno iddynt wrth lofnodi’r <abbr title=\"atwrneiaeth "
"arhosol\">LPA</abbr>. Er enghraifft, mae’n rhaid i chi wastad:"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/actor-terms-of-use.html.twig:59
msgid ""
"follow the principles of the\n"
"                            <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://www.gov.uk/"
"government/publications/mental-capacity-act-code-of-practice\">Mental Capacity Act</"
"a>"
msgstr ""
"ddilyn egwyddorion y \n"
"<a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/mental-"
"capacity-act-code-of-practice.cy\">Ddeddf Galluedd Meddyliol</a>"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/actor-terms-of-use.html.twig:64
msgid ""
"take into account any instructions or preferences the donor set out in their <abbr "
"title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr>"
msgstr ""
"cymryd i ystyriaeth unrhyw gyfarwyddiadau neu ddewisiadau y bu i’r rhoddwr eu nodi "
"yn eu <abbr title=\"atwrneiaeth arhosol\">LPA</abbr>"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/actor-terms-of-use.html.twig:66
msgid "act in the best interests of the donor"
msgstr "gweithredu er lles gorau’r rhoddwr"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/actor-terms-of-use.html.twig:68
msgid "Your account security"
msgstr "Diogelu eich cyfrif"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/actor-terms-of-use.html.twig:70
msgid ""
"When you create an online account for this service, use a valid email address and "
"choose a strong password that\n"
"                        someone else will not be able to guess easily."
msgstr ""
"Pan fyddwch yn creu cyfrif ar-lein ar gyfer y gwasanaeth hwn, defnyddiwch gyfeiriad "
"e-bost dilys a defnyddiwch gyfrinair cadarn na all \n"
"                        rhywun arall ddyfalu beth ydyw yn hawdd."

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/actor-terms-of-use.html.twig:76
msgid ""
"It’s your responsibility to keep your sign-in details safe. You should not use a "
"shared email address to create your account.\n"
"                        Do not share your password with anyone or write it down."
msgstr ""
"Eich cyfrifoldeb chi yw cadw eich manylion mewngofnodi yn ddiogel. Ni ddylech "
"ddefnyddio cyfeiriad e-bost rydych yn ei rannu â rhywun arall i greu eich cyfrif.\n"
"                        Peidiwch â rhannu eich cyfrinair gyda neb neu ei ysgrifennu "
"ar ddarn o bapur."

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/actor-terms-of-use.html.twig:82
msgid ""
"You’re responsible for all activity on your Use a lasting power of attorney service "
"account. We keep a record of\n"
"                        activity for security and anti-fraud purposes."
msgstr ""
"Chi sy’n gyfrifol am yr holl weithgaredd ar eich cyfrif gwasanaeth Defnyddio "
"atwrneiaeth arhosol. Rydym yn cadw cofnod o’ch \n"
"                        gweithgaredd at ddibenion diogelwch ac i atal twyll."

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/actor-terms-of-use.html.twig:88
msgid ""
"We recommend that you sign out of your account when you’re not using the service. "
"We’ll automatically sign\n"
"                        you out if you’ve not used the service for 60 minutes."
msgstr ""
"Rydym yn argymell eich bod yn allgofnodi o’ch cyfrif pan nad ydych yn defnyddio’r "
"gwasanaeth. Byddwn yn eich allgofnodi’n awtomatig \n"
"                        os nad ydych wedi defnyddio’r gwasanaeth am 60 munud."

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/actor-terms-of-use.html.twig:94
msgid ""
"If you download or print a copy of the <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney"
"\">LPA</abbr>\n"
"                        summary, make sure you keep the information safe and secure."
msgstr ""
"Os ydych yn lawrlwytho neu’n argraffu copi o grynodeb ar-lein yr <abbr title="
"\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr>,\n"
"                        gwnewch yn siŵr eich bod yn cadw’r wybodaeth yn saff ac yn "
"ddiogel."

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/actor-terms-of-use.html.twig:99
msgid "Use access codes responsibly"
msgstr "Defnyddio codau mynediad yn gyfrifol"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/actor-terms-of-use.html.twig:101
msgid ""
"When you give someone an <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr> access "
"code, you’re giving them access\n"
"                        to personal information about the donor and attorneys on an "
